	<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Chef's Special: Braised Chicken]]></title>
		<link>https://example.com/chefs-special-braised-chicken/</link>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Our signature braised chicken is slow-cooked for over four hours in a rich herb-infused sauce, resulting in a dish that is tender, flavorful, and deeply satisfying. Each plate is carefully arranged and garnished with fresh parsley.</p><p>The secret lies in our house-made sauce — a blend of roasted garlic, white wine, thyme and rosemary that has been perfected over years. Served alongside golden potato gnocchi, this dish represents everything we believe fine dining should be.</p>]]></content:encoded>
