	<item>
		<title><![CDATA[The Art of Perfect Pasta]]></title>
		<link>https://example.com/the-art-of-perfect-pasta/</link>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>There is something timeless about a perfectly made plate of pasta. Our Spaghetti al Pesto is made fresh every morning using basil grown in our own herb garden, combined with aged Parmesan and the finest cold-pressed olive oil.</p><p>We believe pasta should be simple and honest — just the purest ingredients prepared with skill and care. The result is a dish that feels both light and deeply satisfying.</p>]]></content:encoded>
