	<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Garden Fresh Avocado Salad]]></title>
		<link>https://example.com/garden-fresh-avocado-salad/</link>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Our Garden Salad celebrates the beauty of fresh, seasonal ingredients. At its heart is a perfectly ripe avocado, halved and seasoned with flaked sea salt and cracked black pepper, resting on a bed of peppery watercress and vibrant edible flowers.</p><p>Each bloom is hand-picked and chosen for the subtle flavors it brings — from peppery nasturtium to delicate violet. Light, nourishing and beautiful.</p>]]></content:encoded>
