	<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Dark Chocolate Cheesecake with Berries]]></title>
		<link>https://example.com/dark-chocolate-cheesecake/</link>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Our dessert menu is a celebration of indulgence. Our Dark Chocolate Cheesecake features a velvety smooth filling of cream cheese and caramel on a rich dark chocolate crust, finished with a mirror-glaze topping.</p><p>Served with fresh raspberries and a berry coulis, this dessert strikes the perfect balance between richness and freshness. Our most requested dessert — a perfect ending to a perfect meal.</p>]]></content:encoded>
