	<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Signature Grilled Ribeye Steak]]></title>
		<link>https://example.com/signature-grilled-ribeye-steak/</link>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Our Ribeye Steak is the crown jewel of our menu. Sourced from grass-fed cattle and aged for a minimum of 28 days, it is seared over charcoal at high heat to develop a deep caramelized crust while remaining beautifully pink inside.</p><p>Finished with fresh herbs and served with roasted cherry tomatoes and seasonal vegetables. Available in two sizes: 250g and 350g. We recommend medium-rare.</p>]]></content:encoded>
