	<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Our Berry Smoothie Bowls]]></title>
		<link>https://example.com/berry-smoothie-bowls/</link>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Our smoothie bowls are a beloved fixture on our brunch menu. Made with frozen mixed berries and Greek yogurt, each bowl is crowned with fresh strawberries, blueberries, raspberries, toasted granola and coconut flakes.</p><p>Available Saturday and Sunday brunch from 10 AM to 2 PM. Pairs wonderfully with our latte art coffee.</p>]]></content:encoded>
