	<item>
		<title><![CDATA[The Perfect Morning Latte]]></title>
		<link>https://example.com/the-perfect-morning-latte/</link>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Coffee at Savoria is not an afterthought — it is an experience in itself. Our baristas source single-origin beans from small farms and roast them in-house every week.</p><p>Each latte is crafted with care, the milk steamed to exactly the right temperature and poured with precision to create our signature latte art. We serve coffee all day, from morning opening until evening close.</p>]]></content:encoded>
