	<item>
		<title><![CDATA[About Savoria]]></title>
		<link>https://example.com/about/</link>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to Savoria — a restaurant born from a passion for honest, beautiful food and the belief that a great meal is one of life's greatest pleasures.</p><p>Founded in 2018, Savoria has become a neighborhood destination for those who appreciate quality ingredients, thoughtful cooking and warm hospitality. Our kitchen is led by Chef Marco, who trained across Europe before returning home to open a restaurant that reflects his philosophy: simplicity, seasonality and skill.</p><p>Our herb garden provides fresh herbs for the kitchen every day. Our suppliers are local, our menu changes with the seasons, and our team is dedicated to making every visit special.</p>]]></content:encoded>
		<wp:post_id>200</wp:post_id>
		<wp:post_date><![CDATA[2024-01-01 12:00:00]]></wp:post_date>
